channel.title: Every custom is nulled
channel.description:
Hey, I downloaded a new cache... won't go into detail but whenever i carry a new item, such as Bandos Warspear, i am carrying a huge fence.
i know that this means my models are unrecognizable or whatever. But, is there a way to stop this? perhaps, replace a certain file from my new cache with my old one so these items aren't fucked...
Suggestion :P
Thanks ~ Dai
